等管道；<br />\n<br />\n6) 根據您要求簽訂和履行合同所必需的；<br />\n<br />\n7) 用於維護所提供的產品或服務的安全穩定運行所必需的，例如發現、處置產品或服務的故障；<br />\n<br />\n8) 為開展合法的新聞報導所必需的；<br />\n<br />\n9) 出於公共利益開展統計或學術研究所必要，且其對外提供學術研究或描述的結果時，對結果中所包含的個人資訊進行去標識化處理的；<br />\n<br />\n10) 法律法規規定的其他情形。"},{"pid":"bcee7f2e1916d0bec33f4240b53caa8be9e15f49","tid":1989270,"uid":76747,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"又話大J黃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef1d1589b0319e6452aec44ac12d39a12ffd3c5","tid":1989270,"uid":58287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcee7f2e1916d0bec33f4240b53caa8be9e15f49","tid":1989270,"uid":76747,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"又話大J黃既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"30萬洗哂喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942e54522c28aebed69975cc2669e54f826ceb9f","tid":1989270,"uid":132027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"大j粉： 睇唔到 睇唔到 批鬥返達哥啦"},{"pid":"4cb4d88ff6738c7597a554a5f8a04f6a0cb8bd40","tid":1989270,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"富途其實有咩優勢?"},{"pid":"49237cb2c9974581cfa65ec78f1107e266efb137","tid":1989270,"uid":132027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cef1d1589b0319e6452aec44ac12d39a12ffd3c5","tid":1989270,"uid":58287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcee7f2e1916d0bec33f4240b53caa8be9e15f49","tid":1989270,"uid":76747,"like":3,"